title: Piet Mondrian Lozenge Cosmetic Bag
description:
Cosmetic Bag developed from Piet Mondrian’s Lozenge Composition with Yellow, Black, Blue, Red, and Gray, 1921 from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

Straightforward lines and a striking primary palette are the perfect way to accessorize this must-have beauty bag.

  • Dimensions: 9 x 6.5 x 2 in.
  • Material: Cotton Canvas
  • Zipper closure.
